Title : Page Loader using HTML, CSS

Description : A page loader is a web page component that provides a loading page overlay when you press a link or button. 
You can add different types of page loaders like spinners, loading bars, and hourglass animations.

File structure : 
1. LodingPage.html
2. LodingPage.css

